name.value: All your base are belong to us

/common/topic/article.blurb: This Base is for all Slam Dunk fan out there. Here is your chance to learn and contribute your knowledge about each individual characters in this classic Japanese Manga created by Takehiko Inoue which has been translated all over the world.
